ABOUT ME

{iconUser}

Hi, i'm Axel, a junior web developer. After getting my Japanese LLCE license (foreign languages, literatures and civilizations), I decided to learn code. And I was immediately hooked. Coming from a literature degree it was very fun to be in an environment with languages again, obviously programming languages are a bit different! I also immediately liked the atmosphere of the world of programming and coding, there is a lot of mutual support and sharing, it's something that I appreciate. So.. I became a full stack developer :)
